text: Victor Polidori (born 20 March 1888, date of death unknown) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's team event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1888 births Category:Year of death missing Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nord (French department)
